headline: Sempra to Report Fourth-Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Earnings on February 26
summary: Sempra (NYSE: SRE) plans to release its fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 earnings results by 8 a.m. ET on Thursday, February 26. The announcement will also include an update on Sempra's five-year financial plan.

headline: SoCalGas Customers Can Access Safety Information, Energy Assistance, and Reliability Resources at World Ag Expo
summary: Customers across the San Joaquin Valley will have access to information about safety, energy affordability, and reliability programs and options during the World Ag Expo, where Southern California Gas Co. (SoCalGas) staff will be available to answer questions and provide customer resources. At the SoCalGas booth, visitors will get information on bill assistance programs, energy efficiency rebates, and pipeline safety tips, including the importance of calling 811 before digging.
